    "Models are often assessed using the CIDER or BLEU measure.",
    "A phrase's structural arrangement paints a clearer picture of an idea than a disorganized collection of words.",
    "A story's textual narration is often accompanied with illustrations.",
    "For instance, a sports headline picture can show the crucial moment of the match, but the writing that goes with it will offer a detailed explanation.",
    "In order for words to have a certain meaning, their interpretations need to be easily understood."
